    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Will books, 1751-1788, of Loudoun County Court.  The will books include the names of testator, list of heirs, and year the wills were proven in court.  They also include probate records such as inventories and appraisements.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
